flowRoot.flowPara: I am a highly motivated System/Cloud Architect and Full Stack Developer with a strong growth mindset and the ability to learn and adapt very fast.

Currently I show IT-Professionals and C-Levels in Austria and Switzerland how they can benefit from the Azure Cloud and achieve more for their organization. This includes all kinds of digital transformation workloads from IT infrastructure, serverless apps and containers to IoT, Machine Learning and AI.
